{"id": "art-222", "label": "Art. 222", "title": "Art. 222: Durata arestului la domiciliu", "slug": "art-222", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 222: Durata arestului la domiciliu </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1139203558\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2183\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1139203558\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În cursul urm&#259;ririi penale, arestul la domiciliu\npoate fi luat pe o durat&#259; de cel mult 30 de zile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2020345482\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2182\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2020345482\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Arestul la domiciliu poate fi prelungit în cursul\nurm&#259;ririi penale, numai în caz de necesitate, dac&#259; se men&#355;in\ntemeiurile care au determinat luarea m&#259;surii sau au ap&#259;rut temeiuri\nnoi, fiecare prelungire neputând s&#259; dep&#259;&#351;easc&#259; 30 de zile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_458490161\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2181\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_458490161\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul prev&#259;zut la alin. (2), prelungirea\narestului la domiciliu poate fi dispus&#259; de c&#259;tre judec&#259;torul de\ndrepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i de la instan&#355;a c&#259;reia i-ar\nreveni competen&#355;a s&#259; judece cauza în prim&#259; instan&#355;&#259;\nsau de la instan&#355;a corespunz&#259;toare în grad acesteia în a c&#259;rei\ncircumscrip&#355;ie se afl&#259; locul unde s-a constatat s&#259;vâr&#351;irea\ninfrac&#355;iunii ori sediul parchetului din care face parte procurorul care\nefectueaz&#259; sau supravegheaz&#259; urm&#259;rirea penal&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_190442756\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2180\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_190442756\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Judec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i\neste sesizat în vederea prelungirii m&#259;surii de c&#259;tre procuror, prin\npropunere motivat&#259;, înso&#355;it&#259; de dosarul cauzei, cu cel\npu&#355;in 5 zile înainte de expirarea duratei acesteia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_529164091\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2179\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_529164091\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Judec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i\nlibert&#259;&#355;i, sesizat potrivit alin. (4), fixeaz&#259; termen de\nsolu&#355;ionare a propunerii procurorului, în camera de consiliu, mai înainte\nde expirarea duratei arestului la domiciliu &#351;i dispune citarea\ninculpatului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_358706628\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2178\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_358706628\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Participarea procurorului este obligatorie.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1700306157\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2177\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1700306157\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Judec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i\nadmite sau respinge propunerea procurorului prin încheiere motivat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1190214590\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2176\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1190214590\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Dosarul cauzei se restituie organului de urm&#259;rire\npenal&#259; în termen de 24 de ore de la expirarea termenului de formulare a\ncontesta&#355;iei.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_415454072\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2175\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_415454072\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Durata maxim&#259; a m&#259;surii arestului la\ndomiciliu, în cursul urm&#259;ririi penale, este de 180 de zile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1976290813\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2174\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1976290813\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Durata priv&#259;rii de libertate dispus&#259; prin\nm&#259;sura arestului la domiciliu se ia în considerare pentru calculul duratei\nmaxime a m&#259;surii arest&#259;rii preventive a inculpatului în cursul\nurm&#259;ririi penale.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_35994839\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2173\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_35994839\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)[textul din Art. 222, alin. (10) din partea 1, titlul\nV, capitolul I, sectiunea 5 a fost abrogat la 29-ian-2016 de </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>Actul din Decizia 740/2015</span><span style='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_936883064\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2172\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_936883064\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(11)Dispozi&#355;iile art. 219 alin. (4)-(6) se aplic&#259;\nîn mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1032776244\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2171\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1032776244\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(12)În procedura de camer&#259; preliminar&#259; &#351;i în\ncursul judec&#259;&#355;ii, m&#259;sura arestului la domiciliu poate fi\ndispus&#259; pe o perioad&#259; de cel mult 30 de zile. Dispozi&#355;iile art.\n239 se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA 6:Arestarea preventiv&#259;</span></b></p>"}